%% Learning Session Status State Machine
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Uploaded

    Uploaded --> Queued: Pub/Sub event published
    Queued --> Processing: Worker starts

    Processing --> ExtractingAudio: Video media
    Processing --> Transcribing: Audio media

    ExtractingAudio --> Transcribing: Audio extracted
    ExtractingAudio --> Failed: Extraction error

    Transcribing --> AnalyzingTranscript: Transcript generated
    Transcribing --> Failed: Speech-to-Text error

    AnalyzingTranscript --> AnalyzingVideo: Video analysis enabled
    AnalyzingTranscript --> GeneratingMetrics: Video analysis disabled
    AnalyzingTranscript --> Failed: Vertex AI analysis error

    AnalyzingVideo --> GeneratingMetrics: Visual signals generated
    AnalyzingVideo --> GeneratingMetrics: Vision skipped / low confidence
    AnalyzingVideo --> Failed: Fatal video analysis error

    GeneratingMetrics --> GeneratingRecommendations
    GeneratingRecommendations --> Completed

    Queued --> Failed: Worker unavailable after retries
    Processing --> Failed: Unexpected processing error

    Completed --> Reprocessing: User requests reanalysis
    Failed --> Reprocessing: User retries
    Reprocessing --> Queued

    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
